  <brief_title>Comparison Study of Operation and PEIT for Small, Solitary Hepatocellular Carcinoma (HCC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Trial of the Effective Therapy for Small, Solitary HCC Comparing Operation and Percutaneous Ethanol Injection Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
