  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to choose the preferred treatment modality for solitary, small
      hepatocellular carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To compare the below things between operation group and percutaneous ethanol injection
      therapy (PEIT) group:

        1. Survival

             -  5 year overall survival rate

             -  Disease free survival rate

        2. Recurrence

             -  Cumulative recurrence rate
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
